OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold start, perhaps frosty,
OL,6,Fbut largely dry with sunny intervals
OL,7,Fduring the morning, turning cloudier
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon. Cloud breaking
OL,9,Fwith some further sunny intervals late
OL,10,Fin the afternoon. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome early evening sunny
OL,13,Fspells before cloud increasing from
OL,14,Fthe north. Band of rain, perhaps heavy
OL,15,Fat times, moving south overnight.
OL,16,FBecoming breezy.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FLargely dry and bright with
OL,19,Fsunny intervals and a few coastal
OL,20,Fshowers. Breezy, though strong winds
OL,21,Fnear coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
